text=%25trail%25%3c%3c|[[Index]]|>>%0a! Miele-LXIV%0a!!11.3.2020%0aCheck your Covid19 CT scan using Miele-LXIV, free and OpenSource.%0a* [[https://medevel.com/ttbyq-lshaa-ltshkhysy-lmjn-miele-lxiv/ | Arabic translation]]%0a* [[https://medevel.com/miele-lxiv-macos-icin-acik-kaynak-ve-ucretsiz-dicom-calisma-istasyonu-ve-goruntuleyicisi/ | Turkish translation]]%0a!!5.4.2019%0aI would like to announce the Miele-LXIV project, a 100%25 DICOM standard%0acompliant image viewer for macOS.%0a%0a!! macOS App store download%0aYou can also install the build binary directly from the macApp Store:%0a* https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/miele-lxiv/id988332475%0a%0a!! Build from source in 5 easy steps%0aIf you want build the project with all its dependencies yourself then%0astart here: %0a* https://github.com/bettar/miele-lxiv-easy%0a%0a!! License%0aThe software is 100%25 free, the License is [[https://github.com/bettar/miele-lxiv/blob/lxiv/LICENSE | GPLv3.0]].%0a%0a!! Article%0a[[https://medevel.com/miele-lxiv-dicom-macosx/ | Miele-LXIV in the News]]%0a%0a!! Special Feature list%0a* Runs from macOS 10.9 to the latest.%0a* Miele-LXIV supports German, French, English, Italian, Spanish, Chinese and Japanese. %0a* Miele-LXIV supports "3D Ball" and "Oval and "Angel".%0a* Miele-LXIV supports DICOM printing 64-bit.%0a* Latest libraries supported: TIFF: 4.0.10, VTK: 8.2.0, ITK: 4.13.2, DCMTK: 3.6.4, openssl: 1.1.0j, zlib: 1.2.11, openjpeg: 2.2.0%0a* Fully independent [[https://github.com/bettar/miele-lxiv-plugin-generator | Plugin Generator System]].%0a%0a!! Miele Worklist System%0a* [[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0DbzPXEXdSk | Youtube Video]], [[https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/miele-dicom-worklist-system/id1088730812 | download]]%0a* wlmscpfs%0a%0a!! Current Feature list[[#FeatureList]]%0a!!!DICOM File Support%0a#Read and display all DICOM Files (mono-frame, multi-frames)%0a#Read and display the new MRI/CT multi-frame format (5200 group)%0a#JPEG Lossy, JPEG Lossless, JPEG-LS, JPEG 2000, RLE Monochrome1, Monochrome2, RGB, YBR, Planar, Palettes, ...%0a#Support custom (non-square) Pixel Aspect Ratio 8, 12, 16, 32 bits%0a#Write 'SC' (Secondary Capture) DICOM Files from any 2D/3D reconstructions%0a#Read and display all DICOM Meta-Data%0a#Read AND Write DICOM CD/DVD (DICOMDIR support)%0a#Export DICOM Files to TIFF, JPEG, Quicktime, RAW, DICOM, PACS CD/DVD Creation with DICOMDIR support, including cross-platform viewer (Weasis)%0a#Built-in SQL compatible database with unlimited number of files%0a%0a!!!DICOM Network Support%0a#Send studies (C-STORE SCU, DICOM Send)%0a#Receive studies (C-STORE SCP, DICOM Listener)%0a#Query and Retrieve studies from/to a PACS workstation (C-FIND SCU, C-MOVE SCU, WADO)%0a#Use Miele-LXIV as a DICOM PACS server (C-FIND SCP, C-MOVE SCP, WADO)%0a#On-the-fly conversion between all DICOM transfer syntaxes C-GET SCU/SCP and WADO support for dynamic IP transfers%0a%0a!!!DICOM Printing support%0a#Seamless integration with OsiriX HD for iPhone/iPad%0a#Seamless integration with any PACS server, including the open-source dcm4chee server%0a#Non-DICOM Files Support%0a#LSM files from Zeiss (8, 16, 32 bits) (Confocal Microscopy)%0a#BioRadPIC files (8, 16, 32 bits) (Confocal Microscopy)%0a#TIFF (8, 12, 16, 32 bits), multi-pages%0a#ANALYZE (8, 12, 16, 32 bits)%0a#PNG, JPEG, PDF (multi-pages), Quicktime, AVI, MPEG, MPEG4%0a%0a!!!2D Viewer%0a#Intuitive GUI%0a#Customizable Toolbars%0a#Bicubic Interpolation with full 32-bit pixel pipeline%0a#Thick Slab for multi-slices CT and MRI (Mean, MIP, Volume Rendering)%0a#ROIs: Polygons, Circles, Pencil, Rectangles, Point, ... with undo/redo support%0a#Key Images%0a#Multi-Buttons and Scroll-wheel mouses supported, including Magic Trackpad support.%0a#Custom CLUT (Color Look-Up Tables)%0a#Custom 3x3 and 5x5 Convolution Filters (Bone filters, ...)%0a#4D Viewer for Cardiac-CT and other temporal series%0a#Image Fusion for PET-CT & SPECT-CT exams with adjustable blending percentage%0a#Image subtraction for XA%0a#Hanging Protocols%0a#Tiles export%0a#2D Image Registration & Reslicing%0a#Workspaces%0a#Plugins support for external functions%0a%0a!!!3D Post-Processing%0a#MPR (Multiplanar Reconstruction) with Thick Slab (Mean, MIP, Volume Rendering)%0a#3D Curved-MPR with Thick Slab%0a#3D MIP (Maximum Intensity Projection)%0a#3D Volume Rendering%0a#3D Surface Rendering%0a#3D ROIs%0a#3D Image Registration%0a#Stereo Vision with Red/Blue glasses%0a#Export any 3D images to Quicktime, TIFF, JPEG%0a#All 3D viewers support 'Image Fusion' for PET-CT exams and '4D mode' for Cardiac-CT.%0a%0a!!!Optimization%0a#Multi-threaded for multi-processors and multi-core processors support%0a#Asyncronous reading%0a#OpenGL for 2D Viewer and all 3D Viewers%0a#Graphic board accelerated, with 3D texture mapping support%0a%0a!!!Expansion & Scientific Research%0a#Miele-LXIV supports a complete dynamic plugins architecture%0a#Access pixels directly in 32-bits float for B&W images or ARGB values for color images%0a#Create and manage windows%0a#Access the entire Cocoa framework%0a#Create and manage OpenGL views%0a%0a!!!Based on robust Open-Source components%0a#Cocoa (OpenStep, GNUStep, NextStep)%0a#VTK (Visualization Toolkit)%0a#ITK (Insight Toolkit)%0a#PixelMed (David Clunie)%0a#OpenJPEG%0a#DICOM Offis DCMTK%0a#OpenGL%0a#LibTIFF%0a#LibJPEG
