diff:1554103188:1554103107:=33,49c33,47%0a%3c #Send studies (C-STORE SCU, DICOM Send)%0a%3c #Receive studies (C-STORE SCP, DICOM Listener)%0a%3c #Query and Retrieve studies from/to a PACS workstation (C-FIND SCU, C-MOVE SCU, WADO)%0a%3c #Use Miele-LXIV as a DICOM PACS server (C-FIND SCP, C-MOVE SCP, WADO)%0a%3c #On-the-fly conversion between all DICOM transfer syntaxes C-GET SCU/SCP and WADO support for dynamic IP transfers%0a%3c %0a%3c !!!DICOM Printing support%0a%3c #Seamless integration with OsiriX HD for iPhone/iPad%0a%3c #Seamless integration with any PACS server, including the open-source dcm4chee server%0a%3c #Non-DICOM Files Support%0a%3c #LSM files from Zeiss (8, 16, 32 bits) (Confocal Microscopy)%0a%3c #BioRadPIC files (8, 16, 32 bits) (Confocal Microscopy)%0a%3c #TIFF (8, 12, 16, 32 bits), multi-pages%0a%3c #ANALYZE (8, 12, 16, 32 bits)%0a%3c #PNG, JPEG, PDF (multi-pages), Quicktime, AVI, MPEG, MPEG4%0a%3c %0a%3c !!!2D Viewer%0a---%0a> Send studies (C-STORE SCU, DICOM Send)%0a> Receive studies (C-STORE SCP, DICOM Listener)%0a> Query and Retrieve studies from/to a PACS workstation (C-FIND SCU, C-MOVE SCU, WADO)%0a> Use Miele-LXIV as a DICOM PACS server (C-FIND SCP, C-MOVE SCP, WADO)%0a> On-the-fly conversion between all DICOM transfer syntaxes C-GET SCU/SCP and WADO support for dynamic IP transfers%0a> DICOM Printing support%0a> Seamless integration with OsiriX HD for iPhone/iPad%0a> Seamless integration with any PACS server, including the open-source dcm4chee server%0a> Non-DICOM Files Support%0a> LSM files from Zeiss (8, 16, 32 bits) (Confocal Microscopy)%0a> BioRadPIC files (8, 16, 32 bits) (Confocal Microscopy)%0a> TIFF (8, 12, 16, 32 bits), multi-pages%0a> ANALYZE (8, 12, 16, 32 bits)%0a> PNG, JPEG, PDF (multi-pages), Quicktime, AVI, MPEG, MPEG4%0a> 2D Viewer%0a
host:1554103188=212.51.146.241
author:1554103107=zeno
diff:1554103107:1553760361:=18,96c18%0a%3c Please let us know if there are any questions.%0a%3c %0a%3c !! Current Feature list%0a%3c !!!DICOM File Support%0a%3c #Read and display all DICOM Files (mono-frame, multi-frames)%0a%3c #Read and display the new MRI/CT multi-frame format (5200 group)%0a%3c #JPEG Lossy, JPEG Lossless, JPEG-LS, JPEG 2000, RLE Monochrome1, Monochrome2, RGB, YBR, Planar, Palettes, ...%0a%3c #Support custom (non-square) Pixel Aspect Ratio 8, 12, 16, 32 bits%0a%3c #Write 'SC' (Secondary Capture) DICOM Files from any 2D/3D reconstructions%0a%3c #Read and display all DICOM Meta-Data%0a%3c #Read AND Write DICOM CD/DVD (DICOMDIR support)%0a%3c #Export DICOM Files to TIFF, JPEG, Quicktime, RAW, DICOM, PACS CD/DVD Creation with DICOMDIR support, including cross-platform viewer (Weasis)%0a%3c #Built-in SQL compatible database with unlimited number of files%0a%3c %0a%3c !!!DICOM Network Support%0a%3c Send studies (C-STORE SCU, DICOM Send)%0a%3c Receive studies (C-STORE SCP, DICOM Listener)%0a%3c Query and Retrieve studies from/to a PACS workstation (C-FIND SCU, C-MOVE SCU, WADO)%0a%3c Use Miele-LXIV as a DICOM PACS server (C-FIND SCP, C-MOVE SCP, WADO)%0a%3c On-the-fly conversion between all DICOM transfer syntaxes C-GET SCU/SCP and WADO support for dynamic IP transfers%0a%3c DICOM Printing support%0a%3c Seamless integration with OsiriX HD for iPhone/iPad%0a%3c Seamless integration with any PACS server, including the open-source dcm4chee server%0a%3c Non-DICOM Files Support%0a%3c LSM files from Zeiss (8, 16, 32 bits) (Confocal Microscopy)%0a%3c BioRadPIC files (8, 16, 32 bits) (Confocal Microscopy)%0a%3c TIFF (8, 12, 16, 32 bits), multi-pages%0a%3c ANALYZE (8, 12, 16, 32 bits)%0a%3c PNG, JPEG, PDF (multi-pages), Quicktime, AVI, MPEG, MPEG4%0a%3c 2D Viewer%0a%3c Intuitive GUI%0a%3c Customizable Toolbars%0a%3c Bicubic Interpolation with full 32-bit pixel pipeline%0a%3c Thick Slab for multi-slices CT and MRI (Mean, MIP, Volume Rendering)%0a%3c ROIs: Polygons, Circles, Pencil, Rectangles, Point, ... with undo/redo support%0a%3c Key Images%0a%3c Multi-Buttons and Scroll-wheel mouses supported, including Magic Trackpad support.%0a%3c Custom CLUT (Color Look-Up Tables)%0a%3c Custom 3x3 and 5x5 Convolution Filters (Bone filters, ...)%0a%3c 4D Viewer for Cardiac-CT and other temporal series%0a%3c Image Fusion for PET-CT & SPECT-CT exams with adjustable blending percentage%0a%3c Image subtraction for XA%0a%3c Hanging Protocols%0a%3c Tiles export%0a%3c 2D Image Registration & Reslicing%0a%3c Workspaces%0a%3c Plugins support for external functions%0a%3c 3D Post-Processing%0a%3c MPR (Multiplanar Reconstruction) with Thick Slab (Mean, MIP, Volume Rendering)%0a%3c 3D Curved-MPR with Thick Slab%0a%3c 3D MIP (Maximum Intensity Projection)%0a%3c 3D Volume Rendering%0a%3c 3D Surface Rendering%0a%3c 3D ROIs%0a%3c 3D Image Registration%0a%3c Stereo Vision with Red/Blue glasses%0a%3c Export any 3D images to Quicktime, TIFF, JPEG%0a%3c All 3D viewers support 'Image Fusion' for PET-CT exams and '4D mode' for Cardiac-CT.%0a%3c Optimization%0a%3c Multi-threaded for multi-processors and multi-core processors support%0a%3c Asyncronous reading%0a%3c OpenGL for 2D Viewer and all 3D Viewers%0a%3c Graphic board accelerated, with 3D texture mapping support%0a%3c Expansion & Scientific Research%0a%3c Miele-LXIV supports a complete dynamic plugins architecture%0a%3c Access pixels directly in 32-bits float for B&W images or ARGB values for color images%0a%3c Create and manage windows%0a%3c Access the entire Cocoa framework%0a%3c Create and manage OpenGL views%0a%3c Based on robust Open-Source components%0a%3c Cocoa (OpenStep, GNUStep, NextStep)%0a%3c VTK (Visualization Toolkit)%0a%3c ITK (Insight Toolkit)%0a%3c PixelMed (David Clunie)%0a%3c OpenJPEG%0a%3c DICOM Offis DCMTK%0a%3c OpenGL%0a%3c LibTIFF%0a%3c LibJPEG%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a---%0a> Please let us know if there are any questions.%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
