diff:1553760312:1553760312:=1,17d0%0a%3c ! Miele-LXIV%0a%3c !!28.3.2019%0a%3c I would like to announce the Miele-LXIV project, a 100%25 DICOM standard%0a%3c compliant image viewer for macOS.%0a%3c %0a%3c If you want build the project with all its dependencies yourself then%0a%3c start here: https://github.com/bettar/miele-lxiv-easy 2%0a%3c %0a%3c You can also install the build binary directly from the macApp Store:%0a%3c https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/miele-lxiv/id988332475%0a%3c %0a%3c The software is 100%25 free, the License is GPLv3.0.%0a%3c %0a%3c The Software has been localized for English, German, French, Italian,%0a%3c Spanish, Chinese and Japanese.%0a%3c %0a%3c Please let us know if there are any questions.%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
